track how many of our home equity custome rs pay only the
minimum amount due on their home equity loans and lines;
however , we can infer some of this information through a review
of our HELOC portfolio that we service and is still in its revolving
period. During 2022, 10 percent of these customers with an
outstanding balance did not pay any principal on their HELOCs.
