At December 31, 2022 and 2021, residential mortgage TDRs deemed collateral dependent totaled $1.8 billion and $1.6 billion, and included $1.6 billion and $1.4 billion of loans classified as
nonperforming and $183 million and $279 million of loans classified as performing.
