percent, 3.08 percent and 0.75 percent, respectively , at
December 31, 2021. The Corporation’ s ALM activities maintain
an overall interest rate risk management  strategy that
incorporates the use of interest rate contracts to manage
fluctuations in earnings caused by interest rate volatility . The(1)
